text: Miroslava Brdíčková (4 September 1927 - 19 September 1957) was a Czech gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:1957 deaths Category:Czech female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:People from Litomyšl
